    "$schema": "http://json-schema.org/draft-04/schema#",
    "type": "object",
    "title": "Problems",
    "properties": {
        "id": {
            "type": "string",
            "pattern": "^[a-fA-F0-9]{24}$"
        },
        "name": {
            "type": "string"
        },
        "author": {
            "type": "string"
        },
        "statement": {
            "type": "string"
        },
        "exaplanation": {
            "type": "string"
        },
        "time": {
            "type": "number"
        },
        "memory": {
            "type": "number"
        },
        "tags": {
            "type": "array",
            "additionalItems": true
        },
        "countAC": {
            "type": "number"
        },
        "countTotal": {
            "type": "number"
        },
        "sampleTestcase": {
            "type": "array",
            "additionalItems": true,
            "items": {
                "type": "object",
                "properties": {
                    "input": {
                        "type": "string"
                    },
                    "output": {
                        "type": "string"
                    }
                },
                "required": [
                    "input",
                    "output"
                ]
            }
        },
        "systemTestcase": {
            "type": "array",
            "additionalItems": true,
            "items": {
                "type": "object",
                "properties": {
                    "input": {
                        "type": "string"
                    },
                    "output": {
                        "type": "string"
                    }
                },
                "required": [
                    "input",
                    "output"
                ]
            }
        }
    },
    "additionalProperties": false,
    "required": [
        "id",
        "name",
        "author",
        "statement",
        "time",

    ]
}

2.1.2.1.6 Problems Target Script
use Online-judge;

db.createCollection("Problems", {
    "storageEngine": {
        "wiredTiger": {}
    },
    "capped": false,
    "validator": {
        "$jsonSchema": {
            "bsonType": "object",
            "title": "Problems",
            "properties": {
                "_id": {
                    "bsonType": "objectId"
                },
                "id": {
                    "bsonType": "objectId"
                },
                "name": {
                    "bsonType": "string"
                },
                "author": {
                    "bsonType": "string"
                },
                "statement": {
                    "bsonType": "string"
                },
                "exaplanation": {
                    "bsonType": "string"
                },
                "time": {
                    "bsonType": "number"
                },
                "memory": {
                    "bsonType": "number"
                },
                "tags": {
                    "bsonType": "array",
                    "additionalItems": true
                },
                "countAC": {
                    "bsonType": "number"
                },
                "countTotal": {
                    "bsonType": "number"
                },
                "sampleTestcase": {
                    "bsonType": "array",
                    "additionalItems": true,
                    "items": {
                        "bsonType": "object",
                        "properties": {
                            "input": {
                                "bsonType": "string"
                            },
                            "output": {
                                "bsonType": "string"
                            }
                        },
                        "required": [
                            "input",
                            "output"
                        ]
                    }
                },
                "systemTestcase": {
                    "bsonType": "array",
                    "additionalItems": true,
                    "items": {
                        "bsonType": "object",
                        "properties": {
                            "input": {
                                "bsonType": "string"
                            },
                            "output": {
                                "bsonType": "string"
                            }
                        },
                        "required": [
                            "input",
                            "output"
                        ]
                    }
                }
            },
            "additionalProperties": false,
            "required": [
                "id",
                "name",
                "author",
                "statement",
                "time",
                "memory",
                "tags",
                "countAC",
                "countTotal"
            ]
        }
    },
    "validationLevel": "off",
    "validationAction": "warn"
});

2.1.2.2.4 Submissions JSON Schema
{
    "$schema": "http://json-schema.org/draft-04/schema#",
    "type": "object",
    "title": "Submissions",
    "properties": {
        "id": {
            "type": "string",
            "pattern": "^[a-fA-F0-9]{24}$"
        },
        "problemName": {
            "type": "string"
        },
        "code": {
            "type": "string"
        },
        "userId": {
            "type": "string",
            "pattern": "^[a-fA-F0-9]{24}$"
        },
        "verdict": {
            "type": "string"
        },
        "date": {
            "type": "string",
            "format": "date-time"
        },
        "result": {
            "type": "array",
            "additionalItems": true,
            "items": {
                "type": "object",
                "properties": {
                    "time": {
                        "type": "number"
                    },
                    "memory": {
                        "type": "number"
                    },
                    "verdict": {
                        "type": "string"
                    }
                },
                "required": [
                    "time",
                    "memory",
                    "verdict"
                ]
            }
        },
        "language": {
            "type": "string"
        }
    },
    "required": [
        "id",
        "problemName",
        "userId",
        "verdict",
        "date",
        "result",
        "language"
    ]
}
